===Noun===
'''onomatopoeia''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]'')

# {{uncountable}} The property of a word of sounding like what it represents.
# {{countable}} A [[word]] which has the property of onomatopoeia, such as "moo" or "hiss".

